            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> securitati perpetu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> Iulius <lb n="2"/>Secundinus <expan><abbr>vi</abbr><ex>vus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>fec</abbr><ex>it</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ibi</ex></expan> et Prisci<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="3"/>Albin<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>con</abbr><ex>iugi</ex></expan> et Romaniae Catullin<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>niugi</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>a<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan></supplied> XXV et Iuli<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> Secundinae sorori et Aur<surplus>a</surplus><expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>lio</ex></expan> Secundi<lb break="no" n="5"/>no <expan><abbr>fil</abbr><ex>io</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Archivolte; nach Kremer am ehesten von einer prostylen Aedicula oder einem baldachinförmigen Grabmal (rekonstruierte Breite ca. 1,90 m). Inschriftfeld in Form einer tabula ansata. Unterhalb der tabula ansata Delphine. Z. 1: Buchstaben D und M stehen in den beiden ansae. Z. 4 (Ende)/5: Secundi/no fil. in kleineren Buchstaben untereinander ans Ende der Z. 4 gesetzt.. (B): CIL III 5362: Z. 1 nicht angegeben; Weber: Z. 3: Iuliae (jedoch im Kommentar richtig.</p>
            </div>
